{"tid":2177838,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"新疆「思想轉化營」見聞","createTime":"2020-08-28T04:08:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-28T04:36:48.000Z","uid":29218,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"8cf80d95c584bddffeaed994645d3b63bd33c9cb","tid":2177838,"uid":29218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T04:08:38.000Z","msg":"內容極嘔心<br />\n<br />\n不相信的事發生在她身上：新疆教師自白<br />\n摘錄兩段<br />\n......<br />\n1990 至 2017 年間，Qelbinur 一直在烏魯木齊沙依巴克區第二十四小學擔任中文教師。即使是 2004 年的雙語教學改革、2016 傳言指有維吾爾人因祈告活動被捕，Qelbinur 均不以為然。以至有同事告訴她，有人帶走成群婦女接受絕育手術，Qelbinur 亦表示：「我不相信這樣的事會發生在我們身上。」<br />\n......<br />\n同年 7 月，原本不相信的威脅 &mdash;&mdash; 絕育 &mdash;&mdash; 終於來到 Qelbinur 身上。她當時收到計劃生育部門的發來的電子訊息，叫她接受免費年度婦科檢查。她認為箇中警告不言自明：「如果不配合，將會受懲罰。當時我在一個拘禁營工作，十分清楚拒絕的後果。」18 日，來到醫院的 Qelbinur 發現，排隊接受檢查的人都是維吾爾族婦女，沒有一人是漢族。輪到她時，所謂的婦科檢查變成強行置入子宮環。<br />\n......<br />\n<br />\n原文: <a href=\"https://thediplomat.com/2020/08/confessions-of-a-xinjiang-camp-teacher/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthediplomat.com%2F2020%2F08%2Fconfessions-of-a-xinjiang-camp-teacher%2F&d=Bx5vHrS2V4FMjGMjdccONi8lxPyN12Ak3mY6G5vlvHI%3D&h=4bfd1328\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thediplomat.com/2020/08/confessions-of-a-xinjiang-camp-teacher/</a><br />\n中文: <a href=\"https://www.cup.com.hk/2020/08/28/xinjiang-camp-teacher-confessions/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cup.com.hk%2F2020%2F08%2F28%2Fxinjiang-camp-teacher-confessions%2F&d=Bx5vHrS2V4FMjGMjdccONi8lxPyN12Ak3mY6G5vlvHI%3D&h=a7b8475b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cup.com.hk/2020/08/28/xinjiang-camp-teacher-confessions/</a>"},{"pid":"e79ae6659e5811c0b52ee33dfde47666bb5412d8","tid":2177838,"uid":281652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T04:08:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b519025c7043b3caf3f854380b1acf04a532aa79","tid":2177838,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2